Tradent enim vos * in concíliis, et in synagógis suis flagellábunt vos, et ante reges et præsides ducémini propter me in testimónium illis, et géntibus.
For they shall deliver you up * to councils, and shall scourge you in their synagogues, and ye shall be led before kings and governors, for my sake, for a testimony unto them, and unto the gentiles.
